Race.SpecificTitle: PW Prop. No. 1 -- 4.97 Mills Renewal - PC - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of St. James, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), continue levy a tax of four and ninety-seven hundredths (4.97) mills on all property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $2,568,600 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2018 and ending with the year 2027, for the purpose of maintaining and keeping in repair the roads in the Parish?

Race.SpecificTitle: PW Prop. No. 2 -- 4.97 Mills Renewal - PC - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of St. James, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), continue to levy a tax of four and ninety-seven hundredths (4.97) mills on all property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $2,568,600 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2018 and ending with the year 2027, for the purpose of maintenance and operating expenses of the public buildings, except hospitals, in the Parish?

Race.SpecificTitle: Gramercy Recreation Dist. -- 4.61 Mills Renewal - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall Gramercy Recreation District, Parish of St. James, State of Louisiana (the "District"), levy a special tax of four and sixty-one hundredths (4.61) mills on all property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $204,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2019 and ending with the year 2028, for the purpose of constructing, operating and maintaining recreational facilities in the District?
